                    Valuation Recovery Upgrades
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
                    Legacy PHP erodes business valuation and blocks exit options. We modernise your codebase safely and incrementally so you regain control of risk, roadmap and valuation.
                    Think of it this way: every €1 you invest in modernisation now can return €5–10 in enterprise value at exit — by removing technical risk, unlocking growth, and proving to buyers your technology is future-ready.
                </p>

                <!-- Service specialisms -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
                    <a href="{{ path('service_php_systems_architecture') }}" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-5 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">PHP Systems Architecture</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Clean layered structures, domain logic separation, and framework-agnostic design.</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{ path('service_automated_php_refactoring') }}" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-5 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Automated Refactoring with Rector</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">PHP 8 upgrades, framework migrations, and custom AST rules applied in auditable batches.</div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="{{ path('service_database_refactoring') }}" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-5 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Database Layer Refactoring</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Schema normalisation, ORM migration, and Doctrine synchronisation with Indoctrinate for safe incremental modernisation.</div>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Who it's for -->
                <div class="mb-10 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Who this is for</h2>
                    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
                        <li class="flex items-start"><span class="mt-1 mr-3 inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center text-white text-sm">•</span>
